world's standards in terms of equipment.

304
00:21:20,311 --> 00:21:21,912
That is not so.

305
00:21:21,980 --> 00:21:25,349
Right now, for example, we're
shooting ten films simultaneously.

306
00:21:25,417 --> 00:21:27,083
Take a look at this!

307
