943
01:08:05,947 --> 01:08:08,115
There's no rush.
Think about it.

944
01:08:08,183 --> 01:08:12,920
I'd really like to see the house
where I grew up.

945
01:08:12,987 --> 01:08:19,059
Something has definitely changed
here.

946
01:08:19,127 --> 01:08:22,897
I can't believe this.
We're finally alone.

947
01:08:22,964 --> 01:08:29,269
To think that, in this yard, I
spent several thousand of my
childhood days.

948
01:08:29,337 --> 01:08:32,773
I recognize it, but, at the same
time, I don't.

949
01:08:32,841 --> 01:08:37,645
I have this strange feeling I'm going
to wake up in New York any minute now.

950
01:08:37,713 --> 01:08:43,518
You know, I can't find our
windows.

951
01:08:43,585 --> 01:08:45,620
It's as if they disappeared.

952
01:08:45,687 --> 01:08:50,491
Maybe I am sleeping?
Or losing my mind.

953
01:08:50,559 --> 01:08:55,262
The window has been bricked up. The
building was remodeled five years ago.

954
01:08:55,330 --> 01:08:58,699
They were going to tear it down,
but changed their minds.

955
01:09:03,738 --> 01:09:05,806
Stop, kike!

956
