958
01:09:08,777 --> 01:09:10,310
Ugh! I smell garlic!

959
01:09:10,379 --> 01:09:14,048
Ugh! The kike stinks of garlic!

960
01:09:14,115 --> 01:09:16,551
You're Sasha Greenberg, aren't
