961
01:09:16,618 --> 01:09:18,452
Yes, I am.

962
01:09:18,520 --> 01:09:20,321
I'm Volodya Listov.

963
01:09:20,389 --> 01:09:22,890
We've got you now, you dirty
kike!

964
01:09:22,957 --> 01:09:25,560
On your knees, kike!
Down, I said!

965
01:09:25,627 --> 01:09:28,696
Do you recognize me?

966
01:09:28,763 --> 01:09:34,902
We haven't seen each other in,
what, since we were twelve or
so, when you moved away.

967
01:09:34,970 --> 01:09:37,337
I recognized you, though.

968
01:09:37,405 --> 01:09:39,407
We used to be friends when we
were kids.

969
01:09:39,474 --> 01:09:43,911
