970
01:09:43,979 --> 01:09:45,680
Repeat after me:
"I am a dirty kike..."

971
01:09:45,747 --> 01:09:48,081
I am a dirty kike...

972
01:09:48,149 --> 01:09:49,249
"I stink."

973
01:09:49,318 --> 01:09:51,318
I stink.

974
01:09:51,386 --> 01:09:52,620
"I am gross."

975
01:09:52,687 --> 01:09:54,555
