978
01:10:00,629 --> 01:10:02,697
Then we used to share a desk at
school.

979
01:10:02,764 --> 01:10:09,970
I, a young pioneer of the Union
of Soviet Socialist Republics,

980
01:10:10,038 --> 01:10:22,349
